Description: Geological file system with append-only storage
 PhantomOS is an innovative operating system environment featuring:
  - GeoFS: A geological file system where data is never deleted
  - Governor: Capability-based security and code evaluation
  - DNAuth: DNA-based authentication with evolution
  - QRNet: Cryptographically-signed distributed file network
  - Anti-Malware: Built-in security scanner
 .
 Philosophy: "To Create, Not To Destroy"
